'''Manellan Jasper''' was a [[Tea/Legends|tea]] available from the kitchen stores aboard the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]] and was one of several drinks served at the [[Hard Heart Cantina/Legends|Hard Heart Cantina]]. It was considered to be one of the finest variety of teas to be produced in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

